{"title":"Curious Creatures Drops New Summer Colors and Expands Sizing","link":"https://theradavist.com/curious-creatures-summer/","date":1721926350000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/CuriousCreaturesSummer.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/CuriousCreaturesSummer.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/CuriousCreaturesSummer.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/CuriousCreaturesSummer.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/CuriousCreaturesSummer.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>We’ve been tuned into Montana-based Curious Creatures and were excited to see their summer colors and a new size range announcement in its <a href=\"https://wearecuriouscreatures.com/blogs/lookbooks/weirdness-of-the-west\" target=\"_blank\">Wild Weirdness of the West Lookbook</a>…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/34_Crew_Full_copy.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>This summer, Curious Creatures is introducing new colorways and extended sizing for the <a href=\"https://wearecuriouscreatures.com/collections/womens-bottoms\" target=\"_blank\">women’s bottoms line</a> with Sun Dog Pant in black and four-leaf clover green and the Ramble Scramble Shorts. The <a href=\"https://wearecuriouscreatures.com/collections/mens-bottoms\" target=\"_blank\">men’s bottoms lineup</a> sees the Sun Dog Pant in two colors and both lengths of the Ramble Scramble Short in three colors. Crafted with a blend of performance-driven polyester, the Sun Dog Pant is designed for warm-weather riding, offering a lightweight construction for maximum comfort and protection.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2584\" height=\"1322\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?fit=1200,1322&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?w=2584&amp;quality=75 2584w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?resize=1200,614&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?resize=2000,1023&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?resize=768,393&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?resize=1536,786&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-25-at-10.47.51-AM.jpg?resize=2048,1048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/12_Copper_Landscape_copy_85dc21bb-cc9d-4f2f-8dcc-8305b7051329.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Notably, the pant’s material uses a bio-based stretch yarn instead of spandex, making it easy to recycle when a product reaches its end of life, underscoring Curious Creatures’ commitment to sustainability. Additionally, the pant features a regular fit, mid-rise pull-on knit waistband, secure zippered thigh pockets, and overlapping cuffs for added ventilation and easy on and off of knee pads.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/sun_dog_short_pink_berms_hero.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Both the women’s Sun Dog Pant and Ramble Scramble Short will now be offered in an extended size range, with the pant catering to sizes 0 through 18 and the Ramble Scramble short offering 0-22. This expansion reflects Curious Creatures’ commitment to inclusivity and ensuring every rider can find their perfect fit.</p>\n<p>Check out the summer lookbook at <a href=\"https://wearecuriouscreatures.com/blogs/lookbooks/weirdness-of-the-west\" target=\"_blank\">Curious Creatures</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/curious-creatures-summer/\">Curious Creatures Drops New Summer Colors and Expands Sizing</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4063c1b4f9893dba80b5301f8b6a57c49e224951dd01262a762e4904a3a77e7c","category":"Cycling"}